      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 114,
      "message": "I've copied the same style used for these variables in \n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=policy/drools-applications.git;a=blob_plain;f=controlloop/common/guard/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/guard/Util.java;hb=HEAD\n\nplease confirm that you want this changed to camelcase",
